ZH: 我的家乡是在省城。
EN: My hometown is in the provincial capital.

ZH: 今天我要去省城办事。
EN: Today I have to go to the provincial capital to take care of some business.

ZH: 省城的风景非常美丽。
EN: The scenery in the provincial capital is very beautiful.

ZH: 我的朋友在省城工作。
EN: My friend works in the provincial capital.

ZH: 去省城要坐几个小时的车。
EN: It takes a few hours to drive to the provincial capital.

ZH: 省城的交通很方便。
EN: The transportation in the provincial capital is very convenient.

ZH: 省城有很多名胜古迹。
EN: The provincial capital has many famous historical sites.

ZH: 我很少去省城玩。
EN: I rarely go to the provincial capital for fun.

ZH: 明天我会在省城见你。
EN: I will see you in the provincial capital tomorrow.

ZH: 省城的人口不断增长。
EN: The population of the provincial capital is constantly growing.

ZH: 你喜欢省城的气候吗？
EN: Do you like the climate of the provincial capital?

ZH: 省城的经济发展迅速。
EN: The economy of the provincial capital is developing rapidly.

ZH: 我在省城念书。
EN: I am studying in the provincial capital.

ZH: 昨天我和家人一起去省城游玩。
EN: Yesterday I went to the provincial capital with my family to have fun.

ZH: 我在省城有一位亲戚。
EN: I have a relative in the provincial capital.

ZH: 省城的夜景很美。
EN: The night view in the provincial capital is very beautiful.

ZH: 你在省城生活了多久了？
EN: How long have you been living in the provincial capital?

ZH: 省城的文化底蕴深厚。
EN: The provincial capital has a rich cultural heritage.

ZH: 我们要去省城看演出。
EN: We are going to the provincial capital to watch a performance.

ZH: 省城的教育水平很高。
EN: The education level in the provincial capital is very high.
